<Title>Entry Door Window Seals</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Any number may be migrated. The seals may migrate to protrude into the airflow, but are not permitted to be missing from the window frame assembly. Consult AMM 56-31-01 to determine if noted seal mismatch indicates seal migration.</Para>
<Para>A migrated window seal will generally be visible in a walk-around inspection without the need to measure actual seal displacement.</Para>
